<seg id=1> China will speed up talented person market system construction </seg>
</hl> 
<p> 
<seg id=2> New China News Agency Beijing on September first electricity Central Committee of the CCP organization department, human resources department recently sent out notice, requested to be strengthened talented person market construction plan, sped up talented person market development step, promoted talented person market healthy development. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=3> Notice points out, cultivates and develops talented person market overall goal is:  Realizes individual independently select industry, unit independently selects person, market adjustment supply and demand, social service is perfect, society safeguard is perfect, under country macroscopic regulating, causes market in talented person resources disposition aspect foundation function. </seg>
<seg id=4> Will cultivate and develops talented person market near future goal is:  Formulates basic policy laws and regulations in nearly 23 years which talented person market movement needs, universally establishes talented person market place in big center city, establishes and develops area talented person information network, support specialized talented person market development, establishment regional characteristic talented person market. </seg>
<seg id=5> Before two 000 years, initially complete function in nation scope consummates, mechanism is perfect, laws and regulations forms a complete set, instruction is prompt, service thorough talented person market system. </seg>
</p> 
<p> 
<seg id=6> Center group, human resources department request all levels of organization human affairs department strengthens talented person market construction and management, strengthens talented person market research and plan, establishes talented person market development overall layout and implementation step, acts as circumstances permit, classification instruction, gradually establishes consummation talented person market system. </seg>
</p> 
